<ng-container *ngIf="groupForm; then reuseFormTemplate; else uniqueFormTemplate"></ng-container>

<ng-template #reuseFormTemplate>

  <po-dynamic-form-fields #fieldsComponent
    [p-auto-focus]="autoFocus"
    [p-fields]="fields"
    [p-value]="value">
  </po-dynamic-form-fields>

</ng-template>

<ng-template #uniqueFormTemplate>

  <form #dynamicForm="ngForm">

    <po-dynamic-form-fields #fieldsComponent
      [(p-fields)]="fields"
      [p-auto-focus]="autoFocus"
      [p-disabled-form]="disabledForm"
      [p-validate]="validate"
      [p-value]="value"
      (p-form-validate)="validateForm($event)">
    </po-dynamic-form-fields>

  </form>

</ng-template>
